<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l12">vns wonhaft Jnnenſıcʒe vnd dıe hab dıe ſıe <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>handen</expan> hab ſein ſey mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l13"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>erbe<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe darcʒu gehörn etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l14">ıſt vns <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>wıſſenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd als Jr vns fürbas ſchreıbt wıe <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l15">Leo Jud klag / daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>ſecklin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſölıch hab entwert ſey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l16">dıe <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dıe <expan>ſecklin<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l17"><expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan> / Dıe ſprıcht / daʒ Jr dıe <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> kein hab entwert </ab>
