<ab facs="#facs_103_r1l22">hett . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheınbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt . von </ab>
